title: Scotch
description: During bidding, the effectiveness of catnip tokens are doubled.
flavor: Always down for a belly rub.

title: Winnie
description: During bidding, the effectiveness of food tokens are doubled.
flavor: Feed me, or the feet get the teeth again.

title: The Zoomies
description:
Draft: Reveal immediately, gain X tokens of any kind, where X is the number of cards left in the draft. You must draft the rest of the cards this round at random. 
Action: Gain 2 tokens at random.

title: Shepherd of The Many
description: Action: Target player spends X food tokens, where X is the number of Strays in play. Gain X points.

title: Seize Pawduction
description: Action: Gain X food tokens, where X is the number of players. Select target player to gain X-1 food tokens. Select another target player to gain X-2 food tokens. Select another target player to gain X-3 food tokens.
flavor: Leninist cat disapproves of your bourgeoisie revisionism.

title: Mine!
description: Steal target item from another player.
flavor: Whats yours is mine, and whats mine is mine.

title: NO!
description: Reaction: Cancel target action. Yes, you can NO a NO.
flavor: I hope to God this means I can avoid explaining the stack.
